What's new

Whats new in Klaviyo

See product roadmap

Get ready to revolutionize customer relationships. Our latest AI-powered features are here to take engagement to the next level.

On this page:
  • Klaviyo AI
  • Klaviyo Service
  • Q3 2025 Release
  • Full update list
  • Klaviyo AI
Q3 2025 Release

Our biggest product drop. Ever.

AI agents that do the work for you. Service that solves customer issues and sells. A smarter omnichannel marketing reality where AI, data, and channels truly work as one. Its all here.

Klaviyo AI

Meet K:AI. Built for autonomy.

Explore Klaviyo AI

Klaviyo AI (K:AI) is bringing faster, automated marketing and service, right where you already work. With K:AI Marketing Agent, you can start sending on-brand campaignsand driving revenuewith just 3 steps, in just 3 minutes, while K:AI Customer Agent works as your best sales rep, resolving issues and converting across all your channels, 24/7.

Klaviyo Service

Support that solves and sells

Explore Klaviyo Service

When your marketing and service are on the B2C CRM, you can turn every support interaction into a revenue driverwhether your customers are getting live support or chatting with an AI agent. Its service, reimagined.

K:AI Marketing Agent

K:AI Marketing Agent gets campaigns moving instantly, then keeps optimizing on its ownso you spend less time tinkering and more time watching revenue grow.

K:AI Customer Agent

When questions go unanswered, sales slip away. K:AI Customer Agent keeps shoppers engaged with real help 24/7 across chat, text, email, and soon WhatsAppanswering questions, recommending products, and clearing roadblocks so more conversations end at checkout.

Omnichannel campaign builder

Managing campaigns across email, SMS, WhatsApp, and push can get messy. Omnichannel campaign builder puts everything in one place, making it easier to plan, launch, and measure campaigns that actually work together.

WhatsApp

Your customers are on WhatsApp. Now your brand can be too. With Klaviyo, WhatsApp delivers real-time, personalized messages powered by your data, helping you engage, convert, and build loyalty in one channel seamlessly.

Customer Hub

Customer Hub is your brands all-in-one self-service destination. Shoppers can track orders, manage subscriptions, start returns, and even get personalized recommendationswithout ever leaving your site.

Helpdesk

Think of Helpdesk as your teams all-in-one support hub. It pulls in email, chat, SMS, and socialplus all your data from Klaviyoso agents can jump in with the full picture, solve problems faster, and turn every conversation into a chance to grow.

MCP server

Now your AI can tap directly into Klaviyo. With MCP, you can connect in minutes and start prompting for what you needwhether its personalized insights, automated reporting, or even full campaign creationall powered by your own data.

Omnichannel attribution

Omnichannel attribution gives you one clear view of whats driving revenue across Klaviyo and beyond. No double counting, no bias, just real-time insights into the full customer journey so you can optimize every channel with confidence.

Data Warehouse Import

Valuable insights like CLV and churn risk often get stuck in your warehouse. Data Warehouse Import brings them straight into Klaviyo ready to power segmentation, flows, and personalization without extra tools.
